pageContext.claim: “A majority of Democrats on the ballot for Congress have already signed up to support a socialist takeover of health care that would destroy Medicare, eliminate Medicare Advantage for nearly 2 million Florida seniors.”
pageContext.analysis: It's not entirely clear what Trump is talking about here. A majority of Democrats running for Congress don't support any single plan that would "destroy Medicare" or "eliminate Medicare Advantage." The health care alternatives they have proposed generally expand these benefits.
